column5: Hey there Heres the link to the report We had a great week-not enough pike action but other than that it was awesome Many thanks to those who gave me feedback either in the forums or through personal messages Most of your spots were bang on! Cheers Gordyhttp://ontariofishingcommunity.com/f...n&fromsearch=1
Thanks for the link....good details on your trip and the photos were fun to look at....bet you'll be back at this camp before too long. Rich B
